ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectProtocol Amending the Convention for the Avoidance of Double Taxation and the Prevention of Fiscal Evasion with respect to Taxes on Income - Singapore ** RATIFICATION **
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to sign, or to delegate powers to sign, on behalf of Canada, subject to ratification, the Protocol amending the Convention between Canada and the REPUBLIC OF SINGAPORE for the AVOIDANCE OF DOUBLE TAXATION AND THE PREVENTION OF FISCAL EVASION WITH RESPECT TO TAXES ON INCOME, done in Singapore on 6 March 1976.
